data.description: OFFER DEADLINE, MONDAY, FEB 26th AT 2PM. Hurry to see this meticulously maintained townhome in the Estates at Elk Run, a lovely community within the desirable South Riding Proprietary.  This exceptional home lives large with more than 2000sf of functional living space, a fantastic floorplan, and an oversized 2 car garage.  The entry level boasts an attractive foyer, with hardwood floors, and crown molding leading to beautiful French doors that open to an office/flex space that is perfect for work from home or a gym.  Ascend the wrap around staircase to the main level with gleaming hardwoods throughout and a flowing floorplan including a spacious "great room" that can be configured as a formal living room/dining room or as a large rec room with ample space for an oversized sectional and big screen TV.  Fall in love with the upgraded gourmet kitchen with impressive cherry cabinetry, specially selected granite, an oversized island with glass front accent cabinets, stainless gas cooktop, double ovens and a pantry.  Doors from the kitchen lead to the deck, a perfect spot to enjoy your morning coffee or entertain friends. Retreat to the bedroom level with an inviting primary suite complete with spa bath featuring double vanities, a soaking tub, and separate shower, the walk-in closet has been outfitted with an organizing system to maximize closet space. The two additional secondary bedrooms are generously sized and share a hall bath.  Enjoy the front yard with expansive common space perfect for playing or pets!  Move right in as the home was painted from top to bottom and freshly carpeted in 2023.  This impeccable residence sparkles!  Not only is this an ideal home, it is part of the South Riding community that offers 4 outdoor swimming pools, 10 playgrounds, 4 tennis courts, a pickleball court and miles of biking and walking trails. The state of the art Dulles South Rec Center features a swimming pool with lazy river, sports courts, a rock climbing wall, skate park, and fitness center - there is something for everyone to enjoy!  Situated in a prime location with easy access to the Dulles Tech Corridor, Dulles Airport, and major commuter routes - 50, 28 and 66.  Award winning Loudoun County School System.  Come enjoy the South Riding lifestyle!  Open Saturday and Sunday, February 24th and 25th, 2-4PM.  For easy front door access, park on Daniel Shane and use front walkway to 3rd townhouse on left.
